Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怒龍號  出動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此大幹一場  我也再無遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後只要前往LOGOS的指定地點遠走高飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了  猛銃號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  剛剛的聲音…
